{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4baf6a7111","title":"王力对新华社的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1358484dd8","index":0,"year":1967,"month":3,"day":3,"articleId":"4baf6a7111","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"大联合","id":"18bf6a78fe","type":"主题"},{"name":"王力","id":"20ebde32a6","type":"人物"},{"name":"新闻广播和出版","id":"268718f23b","type":"主题"},{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"夺权和一月革命","id":"714adabb18","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"fa147b61e7","name":"王力"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"74a8e4a494","type":"title","text":"王力对新华社的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4baf6a7111","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"379911001e","type":"paragraph","text":"一、宣传正确对待干部问题，不要只是注意团结，忽视斗争，在斗争中求团结。没有亮相的，有错误的，没有检查的求团结没有好处。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4baf6a7111","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"681149faf7","type":"paragraph","text":"二、凡是闹小团体的，不管经验多么好，不组织他们写文章。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4baf6a7111","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3fd600c3cb","type":"paragraph","text":"三、加强\"抓革命、促生产\"的报导，要把夺权后生产建设方面的成就充分反映出来，要写工人的劳动热情，思想革命化和干劲，也要写崭新的生产面貌，注意第一季度完成计划的单位，要进行报导，春耕生产的报导要压倒一切，要抓好。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4baf6a7111","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e37a83defb","type":"paragraph","text":"四、夺权地区要充分报导，不一定要求那么好，看出是个经验就可报导，不要那么严格。没有夺权的地区，一般不报导。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4baf6a7111","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d5cd2163f5","type":"paragraph","text":"五、\"三结合\"的经验，要报导得更充分，更细致些，特别是团结大多数的经验。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4baf6a7111","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"61b0c6280c","type":"paragraph","text":"六、在报导中不提建立新政权，只提临时权力机构；不提巩固新政权，也不要提全面大夺权。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4baf6a7111","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"930eaa25d8","type":"paragraph","text":"七、各地新华社和《人民日报》派出的记者，不介入革命组织的辩论，不能支持一方打击一方，这样作的立即撤回。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4baf6a7111","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"717287f903","type":"paragraph","text":"八、革命组织内部整风，不作全面报导，开门整风不报导。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4baf6a7111","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}